msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs0.4"
msgid "Bhūtagāmavagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs0.5"
msgid "15. Dutiyasenāsanasikkhāpada"
msgstr "Monks’ Confession 15: the second training rule on furniture"

#. </h1></div><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Origin story"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.41"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pc.15.1"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="BD.2.243"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa400"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.1"
msgid "Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in the Jeta Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena sattarasavaggiyā bhikkhū sahāyakā honti."
msgstr "At that time the monks from the group of seventeen were friends."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.3"
msgid "Te vasantāpi ekatova vasanti, pakkamantāpi ekatova pakkamanti."
msgstr "The lived together, and when departing they departed together."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.4"
msgid "Te aññatarasmiṃ saṃghike vihāre seyyaṃ santharitvā taṃ pakkamantā neva uddhariṃsu na uddharāpesuṃ, anāpucchā pakkamiṃsu."
msgstr "On one occasion they put out bedding in a dwelling belonging to the Order, but then left without putting it away, getting it put away, or telling anyone."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.5"
msgid "Senāsanaṃ upacikāhi khāyitaṃ hoti."
msgstr "And the bedding was eaten by termites."

#. </p><p> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.6"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū appicchā … pe …"
msgstr "The monks of few desires …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.7"
msgid "te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "complained and criticized them,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.8"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma sattarasavaggiyā bhikkhū saṃghike vihāre seyyaṃ santharitvā taṃ pakkamantā neva uddharissanti na uddharāpessanti, anāpucchā pakkamissanti, senāsanaṃ upacikāhi khāyitan”ti."
msgstr "“How can those monks from the group of seventeen put out bedding in a dwelling belonging to the Order, and then leave without putting it away, getting it put away, or telling anyone? It gets eaten by termites.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa401"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.9"
msgid "Atha kho te bhikkhū sattarasavaggiye bhikkhū anekapariyāyena vigarahitvā bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ … pe …"
msgstr "After criticizing those monks in many ways, they told the Master.…"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.10"
msgid "“saccaṃ kira, bhikkhave, sattarasavaggiyā bhikkhū saṃghike vihāre seyyaṃ santharitvā taṃ pakkamantā neva uddhariṃsu na uddharāpesuṃ, anāpucchā pakkamiṃsu, senāsanaṃ upacikāhi khāyitan”ti?"
msgstr "“Is it true, monks, that those monks are acting in that way?”"

#. </p><p> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.11"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

#. </p><p> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.12"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha criticized them, “…"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.13"
msgid "kathañhi nāma te, bhikkhave, moghapurisā saṃghike vihāre seyyaṃ santharitvā taṃ pakkamantā neva uddharissanti na uddharāpessanti, anāpucchā pakkamissanti, senāsanaṃ upacikāhi khāyitaṃ."
msgstr "How can those foolish men put out bedding in a dwelling belonging to the Order, and then leave without putting it away, getting it put away, or telling anyone, and thereby the bedding gets eaten by termites?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.14"
msgid "Netaṃ, bhikkhave, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.15"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:"

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.15a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Final ruling"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa402"></a>
#. <span class="rule"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.16"
msgid "“Yo pana bhikkhu saṃghike vihāre seyyaṃ santharitvā vā santharāpetvā vā taṃ pakkamanto neva uddhareyya na uddharāpeyya, anāpucchaṃ vā gaccheyya, pācittiyan”ti."
msgstr "‘If a monk puts out bedding in a dwelling belonging to the Order, or gets it put out, and he then leaves without putting it away, getting it put away, or telling anyone, he commits an offense entailing confession.’”"

#. </span> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs1.17"
msgid "(<em>15</em>:<strong>64</strong>)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Definitions"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pc.15.2"></a>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pc.15.2.1"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="BD.2.244"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa403"></a><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.1"
msgid "Yo panāti"
msgstr "A:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.2"
msgid "yo yādiso … pe …"
msgstr "whoever …"

#. </span>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.3"
msgid "bhikkhūti"
msgstr "Monk:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.4"
msgid "… pe …ayaṃ imasmiṃ atthe adhippeto bhikkhūti."
msgstr "…The monk who has been given the full ordination by a complete Order through a procedure consisting of one motion and three announcements that is unchallengeable and fit to stand—this sort of monk is meant in this case."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a>
#. <a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa404"></a><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.5"
msgid "Saṃghiko nāma"
msgstr "A dwelling belonging to the Order:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.6"
msgid "vihāro saṃghassa dinno hoti pariccatto."
msgstr "given to the Order, given up to the Order."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="6"></a>
#. <a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa405"></a><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.7"
msgid "Seyyaṃ nāma"
msgstr "Bedding:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.8"
msgid "bhisi, cimilikā uttarattharaṇaṃ, bhūmattharaṇaṃ, taṭṭikā, cammakhaṇḍo, nisīdanaṃ, paccattharaṇaṃ, tiṇasanthāro, paṇṇasanthāro."
msgstr "a mattress, a mat underlay, a blanket, a floor cover, a straw mat, a leather covering, a sitting-mat, a bed sheet, a spread of grass, a spread of leaves."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="7"></a>
#. <a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa406"></a><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.9"
msgid "Santharitvāti"
msgstr "Puts out:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.10"
msgid "sayaṃ santharitvā."
msgstr "puts out oneself."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="8"></a>
#. <a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa407"></a><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.11"
msgid "Santharāpetvāti"
msgstr "Gets […] put out:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.12"
msgid "aññaṃ santharāpetvā."
msgstr "gets another to put out."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="9"></a>
#. <a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa408"></a><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.13"
msgid "Taṃ pakkamanto neva uddhareyyāti"
msgstr "Leaves without putting it away:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.14"
msgid "na sayaṃ uddhareyya."
msgstr "he does not put it away himself."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="10"></a>
#. <a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa409"></a><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.15"
msgid "Na uddharāpeyyāti"
msgstr "Getting it put away:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.16"
msgid "na aññaṃ uddharāpeyya."
msgstr "he does not get another to put it away."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="11"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.42"></a>
#. <a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa410"></a><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.17"
msgid "Anāpucchaṃ vā gaccheyyāti"
msgstr "Or telling anyone:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.18"
msgid "bhikkhuṃ vā sāmaṇeraṃ vā ārāmikaṃ vā anāpucchā parikkhittassa ārāmassa parikkhepaṃ atikkamantassa āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr "if he does not tell a monk, a novice monk, or a  monastery worker, and he crosses the boundary of an enclosed monastery, he commits an offense entailing confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.1.19"
msgid "Aparikkhittassa ārāmassa upacāraṃ atikkamantassa āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr "If he goes beyond the vicinity of an unenclosed monastery, he commits an offense entailing confession."

#. </span>
#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.2.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Permutations"

#. </h2><p><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pc.15.2.2"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.2.1"
msgid "Saṃghike saṃghikasaññī seyyaṃ santharitvā vā santharāpetvā vā taṃ pakkamanto neva uddhareyya na uddharāpeyya, anāpucchaṃ vā gaccheyya, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr "If it belongs to the Order, and he perceives it as belonging to the Order, and he puts out bedding there or gets it put out, and he then leaves without putting it away or getting it put away or telling anyone, he commits an offense entailing confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.2.2"
msgid "Saṃghike vematiko seyyaṃ santharitvā vā santharāpetvā vā taṃ pakkamanto neva uddhareyya na uddharāpeyya, anāpucchaṃ vā gaccheyya, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr "If it belongs to the Order, but he is unsure if it does, and he puts out bedding there or gets it put out, and he then leaves without putting it away or getting it put away or telling anyone, he commits an offense entailing confession."

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="BD.2.245"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.2.3"
msgid "Saṃghike puggalikasaññī seyyaṃ santharitvā vā santharāpetvā vā taṃ pakkamanto neva uddhareyya na uddharāpeyya, anāpucchaṃ vā gaccheyya, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr "If it belongs to the Order, but he perceives it as belonging to an individual, and he puts out bedding there or gets it put out, and he then leaves without putting it away or getting it put away or telling anyone, he commits an offense entailing confession."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="12"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa411"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.2.4"
msgid "Vihārassa upacāre vā upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ vā maṇḍape vā rukkhamūle vā seyyaṃ santharitvā vā santharāpetvā vā taṃ pakkamanto neva uddhareyya na uddharāpeyya, anāpucchaṃ vā gaccheyya, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If he puts out bedding, or gets it put out, in the vicinity of a dwelling, in the assembly-hall, under a roof-cover, or at the foot of a tree, and he then leaves without putting it away or getting it put away or telling anyone, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.2.5"
msgid "Mañcaṃ vā pīṭhaṃ vā vihāre vā vihārassūpacāre vā upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ vā maṇḍape vā rukkhamūle vā santharitvā vā santharāpetvā vā taṃ pakkamanto neva uddhareyya na uddharāpeyya, anāpucchaṃ vā gaccheyya, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If he puts out a bed or a bench, or gets it put out, in a dwelling, in the vicinity of a dwelling, in the assembly-hall, under a roof-cover, or at the foot of a tree, and he then leaves without putting it away or getting it put away or telling anyone, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="13"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa412"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.2.6"
msgid "Puggalike saṃghikasaññī, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If it belongs to an individual, but he perceives it as belonging to the Order, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.2.7"
msgid "Puggalike vematiko, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If it belongs to an individual, but he is unsure if it does, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.2.8"
msgid "Puggalike puggalikasaññī aññassa puggalike āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If it belongs to an individual, and he perceives it as belonging to an individual, but that individual is not himself, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.2.9"
msgid "Attano puggalike anāpatti."
msgstr "If it belongs to himself, there is no offense."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.3.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Non-offenses"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="14"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pc.15.2.3"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa413"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.3.1"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr "There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.3.2"
msgid "uddharitvā gacchati,"
msgstr "if he leaves after putting it away;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.3.3"
msgid "uddharāpetvā gacchati,"
msgstr "if he leaves after getting it put away;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.3.4"
msgid "āpucchaṃ gacchati,"
msgstr "if he leaves after telling someone;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.3.5"
msgid "kenaci palibuddhaṃ hoti,"
msgstr "if the bedding is obstructed;"

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="BD.2.246"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.3.6"
msgid "sāpekkho gantvā tattha ṭhito āpucchati,"
msgstr "if he abandons his intention to return, and at that spot tells someone;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.3.7"
msgid "kenaci palibuddho hoti,"
msgstr "if he is obstructed;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.3.8"
msgid "āpadāsu,"
msgstr "if there are dangers;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.3.9"
msgid "ummattakassa,"
msgstr "if he is insane;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.3.10"
msgid "ādikammikassāti."
msgstr "if he is the first offender."

#. </p><hr><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="15"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa414"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc15:pts-cs2.3.11"
msgid "Dutiyasenāsanasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ pañcamaṃ."
msgstr "The fifth rule, the second training rule on furniture, is finished."

